ABAHOLI bamaqembu aphikisayo kuMasipala weTheku okuyiDemocratic Alliance (DA), Inkatha Freedom Party (IFP) kanye ne-Abantu Batho Congress (ABC) bayikhahlele ngazo zombili inkulumo yesabelo-mali eyethulwe yiMeya yeTheku ngoLwesibili, e-Inkosi Albert Luthuli International Convention Centre (ICC), eThekwini, neqale ngemuva kwesikhathi. IMEYA yeTheku, uKhansela Mxolisi Kaunda, ubethula inkulumo yesabelomali ngaphansi kwengqikithi ethi “ubumbano nokubumbana, ekwakheni umnotho othuthukayo wokubumbana komphakathi, intuthuko egxile kubantu kanye nokukhula okudidiyelwe kwedolobha lethu”. Echaza kabanzi ngomsebenzi wengqalasizinda yamanzi okuhloswe ngawo ukuthuthukisa ukuhlinzekwa kwamanzi emiphakathini yasemakhaya nasemalokishini njengaseMbumbulu, eNgonyameni, eNanda, eNtuzuma, eMnini naKwaMakhutha, uKaunda uthe inqubekela phambili iyabonakala nakuba iphazanyiswe yizikhukhula zakamuva. UKaunda uthe isabelomali sonyaka wezimali ka-2022/23 silinganiselwa ezigidini ezi-R5.6 kwathi ngemuva kwalokho u-R4.9bn ngo-2023/24, nesihlinzeko sika-R5.1bn sonyaka wezimali ka-2024/25. “Ukulungiswa kwendawo yokugcina amanzi iDurban Heights Water Reservoir kuzophothulwa ungakapheli uJuni. Ukushintshwa komsele wamanzi ukuze kwandiswe ukuphakelwa kwamanzi eMlazi Water Reservoir kuzobiza imali elinganiselwa ezigidini ezingu-R892. “Ukuthuthukiswa kwesiteshi esiseMbumbulu sePump Station kuzophothulwa ngo-2024. Kunokuthuthukiswa kokwakhiwa kwedamu laseMkhomazi elibiza u-R28bn kanye ne-Lower Umkhomazi Water Scheme okuzophothulwa ngo-2025, kanti ukuthuthukiswa kwe-Hazelmere Water Reservoir okuzoqala ngonyaka ozayo kuzobiza. R70m. Uhlelo lwezimo eziphuthumayo iLovu River Emergency Scheme oseluqalile luzophothulwa ngoFebhuwari wonyaka ozayo,” kusho uKaunda. Uthe umasipala usuzongenelela endaweni yaseMlazi naseNgonyameni, lapho kuhlinzekwe khona u-R67m ukuze kufakwe iphrojekthi ye-Southern Aqueduct kanye ne-Inwabi ukuya eNgonyameni. “EMzinyathi idolobha likhiphe u-R29m wezinhlelo zamanzi emaQadini, u-R27m ubekelwe ukwakhiwa kwesigaba sokungena eZwelibomvu, u-R8m weReservoir waseNtuzuma kanye nokuthuthukiswa kwesiteshi sokumpompa amanzi; U-R2.5m ubekelwe eceleni ukuze uMnini athuthukise indawo yokugcina amanzi e-Amagcino kanye nokufakwa kwamaphampu amanzi ukuze kuthuthukiswe ukutholakala kwamanzi ezindaweni eziphakeme. “EMfume,” kusho uKaunda, “umasipala uzotshala u-R31m ukuze kuthuthukiswe ingqalasizinda yamanzi kule ndawo. KwaMakhutha, Adams, Mbumbulu naseFolweni, sibeke u-R54m wokufaka i-inlet main kanye nokuthuthukiswa kwamadamu amabili amanzi.” Uthe abaphathi bakhe bazolungisa ipayipi laKwanyuswa kanye namadamu iThandokuhle neKwanqetho abize u-R59m, wengeza ngokuthi kwabelwe u-R15m wokumba ama-boreholes kuwo wonke umasipala. “Onyakeni wezimali ka-2022/23 umasipala uzofaka ugesi ezindaweni ezingu-24 okubalwa kuzo uMshayazafe, Amatikwe, Tshelimnyama, Emmaus kanye neBottlebrush ngemali elinganiselwa ku-R51m. Kwabelwe u-R40m ukushintsha ama-transformer awonakele.” Mayelana nokunyuswa kwama-rate kanye nentela, uKaunda uthe intela yentela yendawo yokuhlala yehle ngo-10% ngenxa yohlu olusha lohlu lwamanani. “Amanzi akhuphuka ngo-5.9% kuthi amabhizinisi anyuswe ngo-9%. Intengo kagesi inyuke ngo-7.47% uma iqhathaniswa nokwenyuka kuka-Eskom ngo-9.61%. Izindleko zokukhushulwa kwendle ezindaweni zokuhlala zingu-5.9% no-9% ebhizinisini. Ukwenyuswa kukadoti ngo-4.5% kumakhasimende ahlala ezindaweni zokuhlala kuthi amabhizinisi anyuswe ngo-7.9%,” usho kanje. Ephendula inkulumo yesabelomali, umholi wekhokhasi yeDA eThekwini, uNicole Graham, uthe iqembu lakhe ngeke liseseke isabelomali, wathi kuningi okukhathazayo futhi okukhathazayo kukhulunyiwe kuphela, kodwa akubhekwanga. Ingqalasizinda yokuthuthwa kwendle yedolobha ibivele isesimweni esibucayi ngaphambi kwezikhukhula, kodwa manje isibi kakhulu,” kusho uGraham. Umholi wekhansela le-IFP uKhansela Mdu Nkosi uthe abantu bakhathele yizinkulumo eziwubukhazikhazi, ezinde zemeya. “Ngesikhathi kunezingxoxo zokuthi umphakathi ubambe iqhaza, abantu bakhala ngokushoda kwezinsiza, kodwa isabelomali sikhombisa ngokusobala ukuthi ngeke sikwazi ukuhlangabezana nalezo zidingo futhi sizilethele abantu bakithi,” usho kanje. IPhini lemeya nomholi we-Abantu Batho Congress uKhansela Philani Mavundla naye uyichithile inkulumo yesabelomali wathi kukhona okungahambisani nenkulumo. Uthe iqembu lakhe lizophawula uma sekwenziwe izilungiso. Eseka i-ANC, umholi wekhokhasi ye-EFF, uMnuz Thabani Miya, uyigunyazile inkulumo yesabelomali, kodwa wazwakalisa ukukhathazeka ngokuxoshwa kwabantu abampofu yiDolobha, wathi lokhu kwenziwa kubantu abamnyama abampofu kuphela ngoba bengenayo imali yokukhokhela izindleko. icala. Ivoti lesabelomali lihlehliselwe isonto elizayo, lapho wonke amaqembu ezophinde ahlangane ukuze avotele inkulumo yesabelomali.